object.customQuery:
select coalesce(Policy_Count,0) as Policy_Count,
coalesce(Claim_count,0) as Claim_Count, 
coalesce((MTDWrittenPremiumAmt+Fact_MTDWrittenPremiumAmt)/2,0) as MTDWrittenPremiumAmt, 
coalesce((MTDEarnedPremiumAmt+Fact_MTDEarnedPremiumAmt)/2,0) as MTDEarnedPremiumAmt, 
coalesce(MTDLossExpense,0) as MTDLossExpense,
coalesce(MTDLossPaid,0) as MTDLossPaid,
coalesce(AgencyCommissionCnt,0) as AgencyCommissionCnt,
coalesce(AgencyCommissionAmt,0) as AgencyCommissionAmt,
Account_Entered_Dt,
coalesce(CededPremium,0) as CededPremium,
coalesce(CededLossPaid,0) as CededLossPaid

from 
(select max(account_entered_dt) as Account_Entered_Dt,
max(Policy_Count) as Policy_Count,
max(Claim_count) as Claim_count,
max(MTDWrittenPremiumAmt) as MTDWrittenPremiumAmt,
max(MTDEarnedPremiumAmt) as MTDEarnedPremiumAmt,
max(LossExpense) as MTDLossExpense,
max(LossPaid) as MTDLossPaid,
max(Fact_MTDWrittenPremiumAmt) as Fact_MTDWrittenPremiumAmt,
max(Fact_MTDEarnedPremiumAmt) as Fact_MTDEarnedPremiumAmt,
max(CededPremium) as CededPremium,
max(CededLossPAid) as CededLossPaid,
max(CommissionCnt) as AgencyCommissionCnt,
max(CommissionAmt) as AgencyCommissionAmt
from 
(select count(policykey) as Policy_Count from 
(select distinct policykey from dbo.policydetail where PolicyInceptionDt <= GETDATE() - 1)x
where policykey not in ('SBP37027088000','SBP37068579000'))BP
left join 
(select count(claimnumber) as Claim_count from 
(select distinct claimnumber from dbo.claimdetail where LossReportedDt <= GETDATE() - 1 and RowEffEndDt > GETDATE())r)C
on 1=1
left join
(select coalesce(sum(LossULAEExpense) + sum(LossALAEExpense), 0) as LossExpense,
coalesce(sum(LossPaidAmt), 0) as LossPaid 
from dbo.claimtransaction 
where
roweffenddt = '9999-12-31'
and date_part(y,LossAccountEnteredDate) = date_part(y,getdate() - 1)
and date_part(mon,LossAccountEnteredDate) = date_part(mon,getdate() - 1)
and BookDt < cast(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP as date))CMS
on 1=1
left join 
(select coalesce(sum(WrittenPremiumAmt), 0) as MTDWrittenPremiumAmt
from dbo.PolicyTransaction
where 
RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31'
and date_part(y,TransactionAccountingDt) = date_part(y,getdate() - 1)
and date_part(mon,TransactionAccountingDt) = date_part(mon,getdate() - 1) 
and BookDt < cast(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP as date)
)PSS
on 1=1
left join
(select coalesce(sum(MTDEarnedPremiumAmount), 0) as MTDEarnedPremiumAmt
from dbo.EarnedPremiumFact
where substring(reportperiod,1,4)=date_part(y,getdate() - 1)
and cast(substring(reportperiod,5,2) as integer)=date_part(mon,getdate() - 1)
) EP
on 1=1
left join 
(select account_entered_dt,coalesce(sum(written_premium),0) as Fact_MTDWrittenPremiumAmt,coalesce(sum(Earned_Premium),0) as Fact_MTDEarnedPremiumAmt from  dbo.Fact_Agg_GW_Premiums
where date_part(y,account_entered_dt)=date_part(y,getdate() - 1)
and date_part(mon,account_entered_dt)=date_part(mon,getdate() - 1)
group by account_entered_dt
)Fact
on 1=1
left join 
(select AccountEnteredDt, coalesce(sum(PaidAmt),0) as CededLossPAid from  dbo.ClaimReinsuranceTransaction
where date_part(y,AccountEnteredDt)=date_part(y,getdate() - 1)
and date_part(mon,AccountEnteredDt)=date_part(mon,getdate() - 1)
and BookDt < cast(getdate() as date)
group by AccountEnteredDt
)CededLoss
on 1=1
left join 
(select AccountEnteredDt, coalesce(sum(WrittenPremiumAmt),0) as CededPremium from  dbo.PolicyreinsuranceTransaction
where date_part(y,AccountEnteredDt)=date_part(y,getdate() - 1)
and date_part(mon,AccountEnteredDt)=date_part(mon,getdate() - 1)
and BookDt < cast(getdate() as date)
and RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31'
group by AccountEnteredDt
)CededPremium
on 1=1
left join
(
Select count(*) as CommissionCnt ,coalesce(sum(commissionamt),0) as CommissionAmt from dbo.AgencyCommissionDetail 
)ag
on 1=1
)MTDLoadBalancing

       dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Master_LossExpense, dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Master_LossPaid,
       dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Master_AgencyCommissionCnt, dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Master_AgencyCommissionAmt,
       dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Variance_Policy_Count, dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Variance_Claim_count,
       dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Variance_MTDWrittenPremiumAmt,
       dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Variance_MTDEarnedPremiumAmount,
       dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Variance_LossExpense, dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Variance_LossPaid,
       dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Variance_AgencyCommissionCnt, dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Variance_AgencyCommissionAmt,
       dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.RowInsDt, dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Master_CededPremium,

       dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master.Source_CededLossPaid
FROM
 dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master where RowInsDt in (
select Max(RowInsDt) from dbo.load_balancing_source_to_master)

object.customQuery:
SELECT 
coalesce(Policy_Count,0) as Policy_Count,
coalesce(Claim_count,0) as Claim_Count,
coalesce(MTDWrittenPremiumAmt,0) as MTDWrittenPremiumAmt,
coalesce(MTDEarnedPremiumAmount,0) as MTDEarnedPremiumAmount,
coalesce(LossExpense,0) as LossExpense,
coalesce(LossPaid,0) as LossPaid,
coalesce(AgencyCommissionCnt,0) as AgencyCommissionCnt,
coalesce(AgencyCommissionAmt,0) as AgencyCommissionAmt,
coalesce(CededPremium,0) as CededPremium,
coalesce(CededLossPaid,0) as CededLossPaid
FROM
(select 
max(Policy_Count) as Policy_Count,
max(Claim_count) as Claim_count,
max(MTDWrittenPremiumAmt) as MTDWrittenPremiumAmt,
max(MTDEarnedPremiumAmount) as MTDEarnedPremiumAmount,
(sum(ULAEExpense)+sum(ALAEExpense)) as LossExpense,
sum(LossPaid) as LossPaid ,
max(CommissionCnt) as AgencyCommissionCnt,
Sum(CommissionAmt ) as AgencyCommissionAmt,
max(cp.CededPremiumAmt) as CededPremium
,max(cl.CededPaidloss) as CededlossPaid
from 
(select count(policykey) as Policy_Count 
from 
(select distinct concat(policynumber,policyversion) as policykey 
from basicpolicy where cmmcontainer='policy' 
and inceptiondt <= date_add(current_date() , INTERVAL -1 DAY)
)x)BP
left join 
(select count(claimnumber) as Claim_count 
from 
(select distinct claimnumber 
from claim 
where 
claim.cmmcontainer='Claim' 
and ReportedDt <= date_add(current_date() , INTERVAL -1 DAY)
)r)C
on 1=1
left join
(SELECT 
sum(case when Reservecd in ('Adjustment') then PaidAmt else 0 end) as ULAEExpense,
sum(case when ReserveCd='DEFENSE' then PaidAmt else 0 end) as ALAEExpense,
sum(case when ReserveCd='Indemnity' then PaidAmt else 0 end) as LossPaid
from ClaimStats  ClaimStats_stg 
where year(bookdt) = year(date_add(current_date() , INTERVAL -1 DAY))
and month(bookdt) = month(date_add(current_date() , INTERVAL -1 DAY))
and bookdt < current_date())CS
on 1=1
left join 
(select 
coalesce(sum(WrittenPremiumAmt),0) as MTDWrittenPremiumAmt 
from policystats 
where year(accountingDt) = year(date_add(current_date() , INTERVAL -1 DAY))
and month(accountingDt) = month(date_add(current_date() , INTERVAL -1 DAY))
and BookDt < current_date() )PSS
on 1=1
left join
(
Select count(*) as CommissionCnt,sum(coalesce(CommissionAmt,0)) as CommissionAmt from CommissionDetail
)agency
on 1=1
left join 
(select sum(coalesce(mtdearnedpremiumamt,0)) as MTDEarnedPremiumAmount from policysummarystats
where reportperiod = DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE(), '%Y%m')
and coalesce(feecd,'') not in ('HealthyHomesFundFee', 'NJGFFee', 'NYFFFee') #exclude CT healthy homes and NJ Guarantee Fund
and updatedt<current_date()
)ep
on 1=1
left join
(select 
coalesce(sum(WrittenPremiumAmt),0) as CededPremiumAmt 
from policyReinsurancestats 
where year(accountingDt) = year(date_add(current_date() , INTERVAL -1 DAY))
and month(accountingDt) = month(date_add(current_date() , INTERVAL -1 DAY))
and BookDt < current_date()
 )CP
on 1=1
left join 
(select 
sum(coalesce(PaidAmt,0)) as CededPaidLoss
from claimreinsurancestats 
where year(BookDt) = year(date_add(current_date() , INTERVAL -1 DAY))
and month(BookDt) = month(date_add(current_date() , INTERVAL -1 DAY))
and BookDt < current_date() )CL
on 1=1
)SRCLoadBalancing
